actions.description: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.
On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to by recorded vote: 232 - 189 (Roll no. 272). (text: CR H4433)
On ordering the previous question Agreed to by the Yeas and Nays: 229 - 191 (Roll no. 271). (consideration: CR H4439-4440)
DEBATE - The House proceeded with one hour of debate on H. Res. 348.
Considered as privileged matter. (consideration: CR H4433-4440)
Placed on the House Calendar, Calendar No. 51.

It shall be in order to consider as an original bill for the purpose of amendment under the five-minute rule an amendment in the nature of a substitute consisting of the text of Rules Committee Print 115-21.
The House Committee on Rules reported an original measure, H. Rept. 115-145, by Mr. Woodall.
